text: Su-Elise Nash (born Su-Elise Michelle Nash on 22 May 1981 to parents) is a British R&B; singer. She rose to prominence as a member of the female group Mis-Teeq. == History == Su-Elise Michelle Nash was born in England on 22 May 1981. She joined the female band Mis-Teeq.
